Today, I head back to Aligarh after 15 days of quarantine. Back to my world. Back with memories of isolation, of uncertainty, and of human triumph. The Delhi skies seem to be bidding me a soulful farewell, with a hope to return soon in better times and health. (5/n) https://t.co/ptpafxpT6t

Soon began the treatment-- a mix of antibiotics and supplements. Ma rushed to be beside me, despite all my pleadings not to do so. Mothers, you know after all.  (3/n)
